commit.message: Added a note about a conflicting django-grappelli setting.
Started 1.2.1 alpha development.
Bumped version number to 1.2.0.
Used the Django's versioning utilities.
Correctly excluded test packages.
Added some keywords to the package's metadata.
Adjusted classifiers.
Converted the README to reStructuredText.
Added some metadata about the package.
Added some extra isort configuration.
Sorted imports using isort.
Stopped ignoring flake8 warnings.
Avoided polluting the global apps registry with test models.
Used TOX to start testing against Django 1.9.
Dropped support for Django 1.7.
Moved tests out the application's package.
Make sure colors are retreived from kwargs.

Merge pull request #29 from budzinski/patch-1

Update README.markdown

Update README.markdown

Add missing colon + adjust indent to sugested by PEP8: 4 spaces.
Use a version of coverage compatible with Python 3.2
